post.description:
Create new a session. Expect an object with `sessionId` props. You can also pass additional [baileys socket options](https://github.com/WhiskeySockets/Baileys#configuring-the-connection) there. Keep in mind that you can only pass JSON-parsable options

Example:

``` json
{
  "sessionId": "john",
  // Additional session options
  "readIncomingMessages": true // Automatically read all incoming messages
  // Additional Baileys socket options
  "syncFullHistory": true // Emulate WA desktop app to receive more messages
  // ...etc
}

 ```

