post.description:
Send a message to someone or group. Expect the below JSON object shape:

``` json
{
  "jid": "62xxxx@s.whatsapp.net", // Target jid
  "type": "number", // Use "number" for number jid, or "group" for group jid
  "message": {
    "text": "Hello!"
  }, // `AnyMessageContent`
  "options": {} // Optional `MiscMessageGenerationOptions`, eg: to quote message, etc
}

```

Please see [this section](https://github.com/WhiskeySockets/Baileys#sending-messages) to learn how to send any kind of message in baileys
